    "description": {
      "value": "<h2>STRENGTH OVER AGILITY</h2>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle1\" style=\"color: #000000;\">Beginning when you choose this ladder at 1</span><span class=\"fontstyle1\" style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 6pt;\">st </span><span class=\"fontstyle1\" style=\"color: #000000;\">level, you can use Strength in place of Dexterity for all attack and damage rolls when wielding two-handed small arms, heavy weapons, or super heavy weapons. When wearing medium armor, your max Dex modifier is increased to 3. When wearing heavy armor, you gain a max Dex bonus of 1. Select either Strength or Dexterity as your warrior ability.</span></p>",
